    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gob Johnson's Downhill Marmalade</strong> is a fast-paced slalom 'em up fantasy roguelite, featuring beloved household name Gob Johnson himself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Avoid obstacles, smash into enemies, collect marmalade boons and do sick tricks.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A Radical Roguelite</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start at the top of the highest peak and race to the the deepest depths to catch the sickest air.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each run down the Great Mountain is different. <strong>Choose your path.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unlock all Gob's friends</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock and play as a bunch of <strong>different characters</strong>, who all have <strong>unique powers</strong>.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Collect powerful marmalade boons</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect Enchanted Marmalade to choose from a <strong>ton of boons</strong>.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Journey through the Radicallion on your quest</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The world of Radicallion has <strong>many biomes</strong> to explore as you descend it's peak. Race down the mountain, skid through the mines, cause havoc in the city and much more.</p>",
